 />\n特別之處係放咗d好細嘅蝦米仔放咗係入面調味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RhJTML0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhJTML0.png&h=7eaa648c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPizza就真係麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上面d料太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9209d3aaed69753b2ac06c3734c71fc59c9db74","tid":2206501,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"個豬手好邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3a688fac0dfe3ed275ee354024060d52618029","tid":2206501,"uid":272819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:36:34.000Z","msg":"luxurious."},{"pid":"4703e36a0ee527c3dc11ac5bd20e84247215ad29","tid":2206501,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:37:44.000Z","msg":"幾多個人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be51e2ef2073660c00a245664a322e0a29add278","tid":2206501,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:38:33.000Z","msg":"點解你餐餐都可以出街食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n極度有米師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad33c2833c78a3e3dbf00d2975070cda7e8118f6","tid":2206501,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9209d3aaed69753b2ac06c3734c71fc59c9db74","tid":2206501,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"個豬手好邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"好耐冇食豬手 事實上我諗應該正常水平<br />\n但我覺得都OK嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/go